{"tid":1376151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不要叫\"香港人加油\"，試著叫\"公務員罷工\"","createTime":"2019-07-28T08:58:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T11:06:55.000Z","uid":171504,"like":172,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"e97c2a0e191fa9fef93b1f962a8d2a048646e36b","tid":1376151,"uid":171504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:58:12.000Z","msg":"車長罷工！可以截斷香港經濟命脈！公務員罷工！可以更進一步逼港府入窮巷！<br />\n<br />\n公務員大罷工，港府就直接停擺，逼政府回應5大訴求。再進一步，呢班高層公務員，AO，EO等本身絕對有能力成立臨時政府/過渡政府，去重啟政改，落實雙真普選！再用公投等其他方法確認方案民意基礎。民間亦有能力成立臨時立法會！可能好ff，阻力亦會好大，但公務員罷工係為我地爭取更多話語權既第一步！亦係突破樽頸既第一步！<br />\n<br />\n都係個句2020立會冇普選，香港收得皮！記住條formula！設死線！唔回應？罷工再設死線！再唔回應再升級！成立過渡政府！解決憲政危機，落實中英聯合聲明中既普選！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68019124a5a6d6498f4040eb69bd80f8c940c35b","tid":1376151,"uid":171504,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:59:41.000Z","msg":"點解2020係大限？下面一片解釋晒：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vGmR3DWT7ho\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvGmR3DWT7ho&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3woeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=f506c6c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vGmR3DWT7ho</a>"},{"pid":"938b590a519a41685455091df60ebc2f7caecab8","tid":1376151,"uid":171504,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T09:00:18.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br />\n寧化飛灰 不作浮塵"},{"pid":"a4076f22b63f5b4134f6ad7bd1260d6bac5a5a36","tid":1376151,"uid":171504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T09:00:28.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br />\n寧化飛灰 不作浮塵"},{"pid":"3373b4e1a333d1727d5943250d0ccdc791478ea4","tid":1376151,"uid":171504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T09:00:39.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br />\n寧化飛灰 不作浮塵"},{"pid":"0c59ed0ba5211c5b61441fe80f0e1ddb79f139d4","tid":1376151,"uid":171504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T09:00:49.0